              "free_text": [
                "Resonances were found at 0.65, 1.02, and 1.35 MeV",
                "corresponding to excited states of the intermediate",
                "nucleus (Be9) at 17.14, 17.43, and 17.69 MeV. The",
                "resonance at 1.35 MeV was found only for the",
                "formation of radioactive Li8 accompanied by the",
                "emission of a proton. Apparently proton emission is",
                "permitted and neutron emission forbidden from the",
                "17.69-MeV state."
